	<td>
	  <font size="2" face="Verdana">
		Subject:&nbsp;<b>RE: Points?</b></font>
		
		<a href="MB_Editmsg.asp?FID=185&FN=Sullon+Zek&SID=7&SN=EverQuest&TID=1872424&TN=Points%3F&CAT=Servers&SURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Eeverlore%2Ecom&MSID=1873210&PL=4&amp;action=REPLY"><img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/btn_reply.gif" border="0" align="right" alt="Reply to message"></a>
